datasets.name: 5df36c01
queryLines:
SELECT 
  sad.*,
  dd.*,
  cm.country_code,
  cm.country_name,
  cm.region
FROM env_catalog.env_data.silver_air_daily sad
INNER JOIN dim_date dd 
  ON dd.date_full = sad.data_timestamp
INNER JOIN env_catalog.env_data.city_master cm
  ON cm.dim_key = sad.dim_key

datasets.name: 51ae33a7
queryLines:
SELECT :`Date Range.start` AS start_date
, :`Date Range.end` AS end_date
, :Cities AS cities

datasets.name: 65ea0680
queryLines:
SELECT 
  swd.*,
  dd.*, 
  cm.country_code,
  cm.country_name,
  cm.region
  , sad.* 
  , gwd.*
  , gad.*
  , gcr.*
FROM env_catalog.env_data.gold_mv_climate_risk gcr
INNER JOIN dim_date dd 
  ON dd.date_full = gcr.data_timestamp
INNER JOIN env_catalog.env_data.city_master cm
  ON cm.dim_key = gcr.dim_key
INNER JOIN env_catalog.env_data.silver_weather_daily swd
  ON dd.date_full = swd.data_timestamp
  AND cm.dim_key = swd.dim_key
INNER JOIN env_catalog.env_data.silver_air_daily sad
  ON dd.date_full = sad.data_timestamp
  AND cm.dim_key = sad.dim_key
INNER JOIN env_catalog.env_data.gold_weather_daily gwd
  ON dd.date_full = gwd.data_timestamp
  AND cm.dim_key = gwd.dim_key
INNER JOIN env_catalog.env_data.gold_air_daily gad
  ON dd.date_full = gad.data_timestamp
  AND cm.dim_key = gad.dim_key
